#

Chickpea Salad with Avocado and Cilantro

10 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickEasy

Description

A refreshing and nutritious salad packed with protein and healthy fats.

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can, drained and rinsed
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • cucumber: 1, diced
  • red onion: 1/4, finely chopped
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
